OL,3,CUS operation to 'surge dramatically',
OL,4,Cas Israel declares next phase of war
OL,6,FAs the Israel-US conflict with Iran
OL,7,Fcontinues to spread, Azerbaijan was
OL,8,Fthe latest country to feel the impact
OL,9,Fas two people were injured in a drone
OL,10,Fattack at an airport, for which Tehran
OL,11,Fdenies responsibility
OL,13,FUS Defence Secretary Pete Hegseth
OL,14,Fwarned on Thursday that US military
OL,15,Foperations in Iran are "about to surge
OL,16,Fdramatically".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/21
