OL,3,CUS operation to 'surge dramatically',
OL,4,Cas Israel declares next phase of war
OL,6,FSpeaking at a press conference from US
OL,7,FCentral Command, he said the mission
OL,8,Fwould "advance decisively," as the
OL,9,Fconflict in the Middle East continues
OL,10,Fto intensify.
OL,12,F"If you think you've seen something,
OL,13,Fjust wait," he told reporters.
OL,15,FHis comments came minutes after US
OL,16,FPresident Donald Trump said that the
OL,17,FUnited States and Israel are "totally
OL,18,Fdemolishing" Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
