OL,3,CUS operation to 'surge dramatically',
OL,4,Cas Israel declares next phase of war
OL,6,FSpeaking from the White House, Trump
OL,7,Fsaid Iran's air force and navy are
OL,8,F"gone", adding that American and
OL,9,FIsraeli forces were doing "a great
OL,10,Fjob."
OL,12,F"Their navy is gone. 24 ships in three
OL,13,Fdays, that's a lot of ships," the US
OL,14,Fpresident told reporters.
OL,16,F"They have no air force, they have no
OL,17,Fair defence. All of their airplanes
OL,18,Fare gone."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
