OL,3,CUS operation to 'surge dramatically',
OL,4,Cas Israel declares next phase of war
OL,6,FHe also suggested that Iranian leaders
OL,7,Fwere ready to make a deal to end the
OL,8,Ffighting, but said: "We want to fight
OL,9,Fnow more than they do."
OL,11,FThe president's comments came as
OL,12,FIran's Revolutionary Guards announced
OL,13,Fthey were beginning a new wave of
OL,14,Foperations against Israel.
OL,16,FIranian state media reported officials
OL,17,Fwere targeting sites in central Tel
OL,18,FAviv, using combined missile and drone
OL,19,Fattacks, in a fresh assault against
OL,20,FIsrael.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/21
