OL,3,CUS operation to 'surge dramatically',
OL,4,Cas Israel declares next phase of war
OL,6,FMeanwhile, the UK stepped up its
OL,7,Fresponse to the growing conflict, with
OL,8,Fthe prime minister announcing he would
OL,9,Fsend four additional Typhoon jets to
OL,10,Fjoin the UK squadron in Qatar.
OL,12,FUS Middle East commander says 30
OL,13,FIranian ships destroyed
OL,15,FSpeaking late Thursday, the head of US
OL,16,FCentral Command, Admiral Brad Cooper,
OL,17,Fsaid the US had struck nearly 200
OL,18,Ftargets in Iran over the past 72 hours.
OL,20,FHe added that the US had sunk over 30
OL,21,FIranian ships.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/21
