OL,3,CUS operation to 'surge dramatically',
OL,4,Cas Israel declares next phase of war
OL,6,FDuring the same press conference, US
OL,7,FDefence Secretary Pete Hegseth said
OL,8,Fthe US had "no shortage of munitions",
OL,9,Fadding that the US mission in Iran is
OL,10,F"advancing decisively."
OL,12,F"We have only just begun to fight, and
OL,13,Ffight decisively," he said.
OL,15,FPresident Trump made multiple comments
OL,16,Fto the media throughout Thursday, the
OL,17,Fsixth day of fighting in the Middle
OL,18,FEast.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/21
