OL,3,CUS operation to 'surge dramatically',
OL,4,Cas Israel declares next phase of war
OL,6,FThe war against Iran is widening
OL,7,Ffurther, more countries arte finding
OL,8,Fthemselves caught up in the conflict.
OL,9,FYesterday it was Sri Lanka and Turkey
OL,10,F- today it was Azerbaijan. ITV News'
OL,11,FEmma Murphy reports from Iraq
OL,13,FIn an interview with Axios, Trump
OL,14,Fasserted he should be involved in
OL,15,Fchoosing Iran's next supreme leader,
OL,16,Fafter the previous Ayatollah Ali
OL,17,FKhamenei was killed during an air
OL,18,Fstrike.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/21
