OL,3,CUS operation to 'surge dramatically',
OL,4,Cas Israel declares next phase of war
OL,6,FTrump ruled out Mojtaba Khamenei, a
OL,7,Ffront-runner to replace his father,
OL,8,FAyatollah Ali Khamenei. Trump's
OL,9,Fcomments to the American news website
OL,10,Frenew questions about whether the US
OL,11,Fand Israel seek the overthrow of the
OL,12,FIslamic Republic or just a change in
OL,13,Fits policies, as the conflict has
OL,14,Fappeared increasingly open-ended.
OL,16,FIn the Axios interview, Trump derided
OL,17,Fthe 56-year-old Mojtaba Khamenei, who
OL,18,Fhas never been elected or appointed to
OL,19,Fa government position, as "a light
OL,20,Fweight."
