OL,3,CUS operation to 'surge dramatically',
OL,4,Cas Israel declares next phase of war
OL,6,F"We want someone that will bring
OL,7,Fharmony and peace to Iran," Trump said.
OL,9,FUK to bolster support in the region
OL,11,FThe UK announced it would send further
OL,12,Fmilitary resources, including Wildcat
OL,13,Fhelicopters with anti-drone
OL,14,Fcapabilities, due to arrive in Cyprus
OL,15,Fon Friday.
