OL,3,CUS operation to 'surge dramatically',
OL,4,Cas Israel declares next phase of war
OL,6,FThe PM said he was "satisfied that we
OL,7,Fcan keep our people safe" as he faced
OL,8,Fquestions about the UK's preparedness
OL,9,Fover the conflict, which sparked on
OL,10,FSaturday as the US and Israel launched
OL,11,Fstrikes on Iran.
OL,13,FAsked about criticism that the
OL,14,Fgovernment's approach had been marked
OL,15,Fby indecision, prevarication and a
OL,16,Flack of preparedness, the prime
OL,17,Fminister said Britain "started pre-
OL,18,Fdeploying to the region in January and
OL,19,FFebruary, particularly to Cyprus and
OL,20,FQatar".
