OL,4,Cas Israel declares next phase of war
OL,6,FThe newly announced resources will
OL,7,Farrive ahead of the warship HMS
OL,8,FDragon, which is due to leave
OL,9,FPortsmouth for Cyprus next week.
OL,11,FIt comes after an Iranian-made drone
OL,12,Fwas used to attack an RAF base in
OL,13,FCyprus, which the PM's official
OL,14,Fspokesperson said was "likely" not
OL,15,Flaunched from Iran.
