OL,4,Cas Israel declares next phase of war
OL,6,FThe relationship between the UK and US
OL,7,Fhas been strained since Starmer's
OL,8,Fpublic fallout with US President
OL,9,FDonald Trump over his refusal to allow
OL,10,Finitial US strikes on Iran from
OL,11,FBritish bases.
OL,13,FStarmer said he respected Mr Trump's
OL,14,Fdecision, which "he considers in the
OL,15,Fnational interest" of America, and
OL,16,Finsisted the "special relationship is
OL,17,Fin operation right now".
OL,19,FIsrael intensifies strikes on Lebanon
