OL,3,CUS operation to 'surge dramatically',
OL,4,Cas Israel declares next phase of war
OL,6,FIsrael announced on Thursday it was
OL,7,Fbeginning its "next phase" of the war,
OL,8,Fwarning it will involve "additional
OL,9,Fsurprises".
OL,11,FEarlier on Thursday, Israel escalated
OL,12,Fits own objective to obliterate the
OL,13,FIranian-backed militant group
OL,14,FHezbollah in the suburbs of the
OL,15,FLebanese capital Beirut.
OL,17,FShortly before 9pm UK time on
OL,18,FThursday, the Israeli military began
OL,19,Fstriking the Beirut's southern
OL,20,Fsuburbs, where smoke was seen rising
OL,21,Fabove the skyline.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
