OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1772884979
OL,3,CUS operation to 'surge dramatically',
OL,4,Cas Israel declares next phase of war
OL,6,FIsrael's armed forces had issued
OL,7,Fevacuation warnings for almost half of
OL,8,FBeirut, prompting frantic attempts of
OL,9,Fresidents to leave the city, plunging
OL,10,Fit into chaos.
OL,12,FThe number of people killed in Lebanon
OL,13,Fsince a resurgence in hostilities
OL,14,Fbetween Israel and the Hezbollah
OL,15,Fmilitant group Monday has risen to
OL,16,F123, with 683 people wounded, the
OL,17,FLebanese health ministry said Thursday.
OL,19,FKurdish dissident groups 'preparing to
OL,20,Ffight' with US support
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/21
