OL,3,CUS operation to 'surge dramatically',
OL,4,Cas Israel declares next phase of war
OL,6,FKurdish Iranian dissident groups based
OL,7,Fin northern Iraq are preparing for a
OL,8,Fpotential cross-border military
OL,9,Foperation in Iran, and the US has
OL,10,Fasked Iraqi Kurds to support them,
OL,11,Faccording to Kurdish officials.
OL,13,FThe Kurdish groups are widely seen as
OL,14,Fthe most well-organised segment of the
OL,15,Ffragmented Iranian opposition and are
OL,16,Fbelieved to have thousands of trained
OL,17,Ffighters.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/21
