OL,3,CUS operation to 'surge dramatically',
OL,4,Cas Israel declares next phase of war
OL,6,FTheir entry into the war could pose a
OL,7,Fsignificant challenge to the embattled
OL,8,Fauthorities in Tehran and could also
OL,9,Frisk pulling Iraq further into the
OL,10,Fconflict.
OL,12,FKhalil Nadiri, an official with the
OL,13,FKurdistan Freedom Party, or PAK, based
OL,14,Fin northern Iraq's semi-autonomous
OL,15,FKurdish region, said on Wednesday that
OL,16,Fsome of their forces had moved to
OL,17,Fareas near the Iranian border in
OL,18,FSulaymaniyah province and were on
OL,19,Fstandby.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/21
