PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1772884979
OL,3,CUS operation to 'surge dramatically',
OL,4,Cas Israel declares next phase of war
OL,6,FIran has carried out attacks on
OL,7,Fpassing ships and vowed to continue to
OL,8,Fdo so, forcing many shipping companies
OL,9,Fto suspend operations in the area.
OL,11,FTrump, speaking from the East Room of
OL,12,Fthe White House, said Thursday that
OL,13,F"further action to reduce pressure on
OL,14,Foil is imminent."
OL,16,F"The oil seems to have pretty much
OL,17,Fstabilized. We had it very low, but I
OL,18,Fhad to take this little detour," he
OL,19,Fsaid.
