OL,6,FTrump earlier this week said on social
OL,7,Fmedia that he ordered the U.S.
OL,8,Fdevelopment finance arm to provide
OL,9,Fpolitical risk insurance for tankers
OL,10,Fcarrying oil and other goods through
OL,11,Fthe Persian Gulf.
OL,13,FPolitical risk insurance is a type of
OL,14,Fcoverage intended to protect firms
OL,15,Fagainst financial losses caused by
OL,16,Funstable political conditions,
OL,17,Fgovernment actions, or violence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G20/21
